<font size=+2> Reading seminar in algebraic geometry.</font><br>
<font size=+2> Spring 2018. Topics in algebraic geometry</font>

<br>
<br>

<p>
This semester the reading seminar will study various topics in algebraic geometry.
Each speaker will present a paper they are reading for their own research projects which is of general interest to algebraic geometers.
</p>
<p>
The seminar will consist of talks by faculty followed by talks by graduate students. We will attempt to make the seminar accessible to everyone.
</p>
<p>
The seminar will meet on Friday afternoons, 2:30--3:30PM in LGRT 1234. 
</p>
<br><hr><br>

<b>Tentative Schedule</b>
